Day 15: Be the Change Agent!
🌱 "Transformation starts with you—be the Agile catalyst!"  
👉 Tip: Advocate for change both within the team and the organization. True agility comes from continuous transformation.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
